name: Genesis
description:
Listen to the birth of humanity. An insidious creature that says hello to the night with the darkness of its inner world. Even though it won't last forever, it still moves forward without ignoring the beginning.

The end is near, but he doesn't really care about that big end. He looks at the sky for the last time. He feels it for the last time and calls out to his beloved darkness, to which he will return again.
